---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="AEO / SEO / SEM" section="aeo-seo">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">07 · Discovery</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Keyword universe + <em>defensive vs conquest.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">"Kleer alternative" and "Membersy alternative" are now defensive (own them as branded). Real conquest = DentalHQ, Pearly, BoomCloud, Plan Forward, Subscribili. Patient-side fights insurance carriers — pick spots accordingly.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="takeaway">
    <span class="tk-lbl">Bottom line</span>
    <p>Own "Kleer alternative" and "Membersy alternative" as branded defense; spend conquest effort on DentalHQ, Pearly, Plan Forward, and Subscribili. Patient-side search means fighting insurance carriers — pick those spots carefully.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="aeo-seo"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="aeo-seo">0 / 0</span> tasks completed</p>

  <div class="callout zest-hi">
    <div class="lbl">Read first — positioning shift</div>
    <p>Per Clerri.com blog pages already indexed: <em>"Kleer is now Clerri", "Membersy is now Clerri"</em>. SEM bidding on these = <strong>brand protection, not conquest</strong>. Cheap CPCs, highest-intent traffic, defensive necessity. Clerri already ranks for "DentalHQ alternatives," "Bento alternatives," "Top platforms for DSOs" — SEO conquest is in motion.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>B2B keyword universe — practice / DSO buyer</h2>
  <div style="overflow-x:auto">
    <table class="data-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Keyword</th><th>Est. Vol/mo</th><th>Est. CPC</th><th>Difficulty</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>dental membership plan software</td><td class="num-cell">200-500</td><td class="num-cell">$12-25</td><td>35-50</td><td>Bid + own organic</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dental membership platform</td><td class="num-cell">100-300</td><td class="num-cell">$10-20</td><td>30-45</td><td>Bid + own organic</td></tr>
        <tr><td>in-house dental membership</td><td class="num-cell">100-300</td><td class="num-cell">$5-12</td><td>25-40</td><td>Content moat</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dental membership plan companies</td><td class="num-cell">200-500</td><td class="num-cell">$8-18</td><td>30-45</td><td>Bid + comparison content</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Kleer alternative</td><td class="num-cell">50-150</td><td class="num-cell">$6-15</td><td>20-35</td><td><strong>Defensive</strong></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Membersy alternative</td><td class="num-cell">50-150</td><td class="num-cell">$6-15</td><td>20-35</td><td><strong>Defensive</strong></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Pearly alternative</td><td class="num-cell">20-100</td><td class="num-cell">$8-20</td><td>15-30</td><td>Conquest</td></tr>
        <tr><td>DentalHQ alternative</td><td class="num-cell">20-100</td><td class="num-cell">$8-20</td><td>15-30</td><td>Conquest (already ranking)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>BoomCloud alternative</td><td class="num-cell">20-100</td><td class="num-cell">$8-20</td><td>15-30</td><td>Conquest</td></tr>
        <tr><td>recurring revenue dental practice</td><td class="num-cell">100-500</td><td class="num-cell">$5-12</td><td>30-50</td><td>Content + bid</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dental membership plan for DSO</td><td class="num-cell">50-150</td><td class="num-cell">$15-30</td><td>30-45</td><td><strong>Highest-LTV — aggressive bid</strong></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:0.825rem;color:var(--muted);font-style:italic">Volume/CPC are dental-PPC-industry estimates (Wordstream 2025 avg CPC $7.85). Confirm in Ahrefs/Semrush before committing budget.</p>

  <h2>Patient-side keyword universe — directory play</h2>
  <div class="callout wine">
    <div class="lbl">Critical Strategic Warning</div>
    <p>Patient-side keywords are dominated by insurance carrier directories (Delta Dental, DentalPlans.com, Humana, Guardian, Cigna) with 20+ years of SEO equity. <strong>Cannot out-SEO Delta Dental on "find a dentist."</strong> Directory play competes on specificity ("dental membership near me") + paid local geo — not national SEO.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="overflow-x:auto">
    <table class="data-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Keyword</th><th>Est. Vol/mo</th><th>Est. CPC</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>dentist near me (root)</td><td class="num-cell">~1.2M</td><td class="num-cell">$6-15</td><td>Don't fight Delta — geo-paid only</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dentist near me no insurance</td><td class="num-cell">20-50K</td><td class="num-cell">$5-12</td><td>Geo-paid + city pages</td></tr>
        <tr><td>affordable dentist near me</td><td class="num-cell">30-80K</td><td class="num-cell">$5-12</td><td>Geo-paid</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dental membership near me</td><td class="num-cell">1-5K</td><td class="num-cell">$4-10</td><td><strong>Own this niche</strong></td></tr>
        <tr><td>dental savings plan</td><td class="num-cell">10-30K</td><td class="num-cell">$4-10</td><td>Comparison content</td></tr>
        <tr><td>dentist payment plans</td><td class="num-cell">5-15K</td><td class="num-cell">$5-12</td><td>Sunbit co-marketing</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>The AEO refresh project <em>(top strategic concern)</em></h2>
  <div data-section="aeo-seo">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-01-press-refresh" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Press release refresh — reissue all major historical releases under Clerri branding</div><div class="task-meta">Targets: Kleer announcements, Membersy announcements, merger, leadership, product launches</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-02-wikipedia" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Wikipedia + reference sites updated to reflect Clerri positioning</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-03-schema" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Schema.org structured data audit — Organization, Product, FAQ schemas</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-04-canonical" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">"What is Clerri" canonical long-form content</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-05-listicles" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Listicle conquest content: "Best dental membership platforms 2026", "Clerri vs Pearly", "Clerri vs DentalHQ", "Top platforms for DSOs"</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-06-faq" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">FAQ + definitional content optimized for natural-language AI queries</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="aeo-07-monitoring" data-section="aeo-seo" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Otterly.ai $29/mo pilot → graduate to Profound $399 if signal real (Workflow B)</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">AEO baseline notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="aeo-baseline" placeholder="Current state across ChatGPT/Perplexity/Claude/Gemini. What's outdated, what's wrong, what's missing..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri/ad-strategy"><span class="dir">← Prev</span><span class="name">06 · Ad Creative</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/directory"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">08 · Patient Directory</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
